{"title": "草部·月季花", "content": [{"type": "text", "value": "草部·月季花"}, {"type": "text", "value": "释名"}, {"type": "text", "value": "月月红、胜春、瘦客、斗雪红。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "气味"}, {"type": "text", "value": "甘、温、无毒。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "主治"}, {"type": "text", "value": "活血、消肿、敷毒。"}, {"type": "text", "value": "附方"}, {"type": "text", "value": "月季花，也是治妇女月经不调的常用药物。"}], "index": 378}